{"tid":518347,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【朱經緯囚3月】朱支持者庭外罵「狗官」　湯家驊：肯定是藐視法庭","createTime":"2018-01-03T08:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T09:53:43.000Z","uid":51904,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2dbc37a0ee65b6786543a968a659520d8c4cb341","tid":518347,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:36:46.000Z","msg":"退休警司朱經緯，退休前在佔領行動期間，於旺角執勤時涉以警棍毆打途人，今午被判監3個月，獲准以5萬元保釋外出等候上訴。朱離開法庭期間，大量公眾人士不滿判刑，在庭外斥責主任裁判官錢禮為「狗官」、「殘害忠良」等。身兼行政會議成員的資深大律師湯家驊回應《明報》查詢時指，「狗官」這類言辭及相關行為，「肯定是藐視法庭」，現視乎法庭會否要求警方搜集證據跟進調查，及往後律政司會否予以起訴。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊表示，公眾可以在公開場合對法庭任何判決發表意見，但斷不可到侮辱法庭及法律制度的程度，否則相關人等也應該要面對相關的刑事後果。"},{"pid":"128ea9cffc10428819ec0084e8f3d66e8386eb2a","tid":518347,"uid":47674,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:40:01.000Z","msg":"唔......思想有所動搖<br />\n雪廠街張相畀佢睇一睇番先"},{"pid":"82a630e55cce27e34608bbe3193d13ca45c88a49","tid":518347,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:41:17.000Z","msg":"判得太輕, 仲比保釋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7e85aaefc9b00c5db1750ff66466c85a51e989","tid":518347,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>淚</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4f09bc86e46b1020c57a2c6b903645524968bdd6","tid":518347,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁串？？我係警犬就爆撚晒當日雪廠街既野嗱！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"feac5c93d6c03532f3660e4419ae23a56baa31e6","tid":518347,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:17